The evidence with the title 'Pandemic alert: Tuberculosis still world's no. 1 infectious killer ' says Oct 30, 2017  ... On monday the WHO released its 2017 Global Tuberculosis Report , and the latest picture is still one of extreme gravity , as progress to stop the spread of this disease simply is n't  ... TB is the ninth - leading cause of death worldwide and continues to be the world's no. 1 infectious killer, surpassing HIV/AIDS. 
